name: Untitled Jet Game
description:
Collect gold, and don't run into other planes.

P.S: Pressing arrow keys might make webpage bounce, I don't have a better fix than to full screen (It appears horribly, though). If someone has something better please tell me.

- Controls -

W or SPACE - Move plane up.

UP - Rotate plane up.

DOWN - Rotate plane down.

- Powerups -

Extra Life - Makes the pilot seat purple, and you don't lose coins if you crash.

Big Coins - Gives you an extra amount of coins.
